{"tid":1130943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建測界22名選委去信謝偉銓　對修訂逃犯條例表達憂慮","createTime":"2019-04-29T11:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T11:08:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7dc0c54aace6e85e5a21594afb43720c7f69a2e8","tid":1130943,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T11:07:01.000Z","msg":"22名建築、測量、都市規劃及園境界選委會成員，向立法會界別代表謝偉銓發公開信，反映對修訂逃犯條例的憂慮，希望謝偉銓兌現競選承諾，保障業界權益，以科學方式諮詢選民對修例的意見，作為日後於立法會投票的基礎。<br />\n<br />\n公開信表示，行內不少從業員均有參與跨境項目，擔憂修訂逃犯條例會令業界暴露於更大的法律風險，令從業員有機會被引渡至一些法治理念不同的國家或地區，這會減少從業員參與內地項目的意願，與政府及學會一直推動業界參與「大灣區」和「一帶一路」項目的目標，完全背道而馳。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1455155-20190429.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1455155-20190429.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9UpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=5ed6eae6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1455155-20190429.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fbdee1c0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1455155-20190429.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"f49f1bbb8f1ed33dd853f1af3bf91ce41c3bc610","tid":1130943,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T11:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}